    <td width="100%" valign="top"><span class="largetext">I kinda like the way they went with the newbie armor. a little trade skilling, and some farmiing and poof you combine you got it. and its descent through abotu 10 or 15. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /> above 15 hit bazaar or find some armor drops. 
<br />

<br />
However, there are a couple nice quests in neriak that will help you out. Right up the dirt steps to the right is a troll names wista. Give her 2 wolf meat she gives you a large bag. So, do it a coupel times it will help yuo hold more. Give three eggs to the troll to her right she will give you a random piece of rawhide armor which should hold you over until you get your newbie armor. Calcified humerous and ribcages are rare drops off skeletons, greater skeletons, and calcified skeletons. Halfling ulna's off what else halfling skele's at the ruins south east corner of zone. or you can find some in the northwest undead area. everything else is pretty much straight forward except the one fish scale, and two bat wings. which you can either bug a druid for. or buy in pok. if you got the silver. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Also, dunno if its a bug. But zerkers are the only class that are not kos to the bandits in paludal. So, should be able to run to paludal around 13. 
<br />

<br />
Hope that helps from the Troll side!</span><span class="smalltext"></span></td>
